There is no BattleTech french official rules in ebook/pdf. With time, few CityTech boxes released at the end of 90s became hard to find.

It's a big work I just finished today: Scan the whole CityTech French book.

I used the Open Source software Scribus to provide a quality PDF with a Table of Contents with direct link to pages.

Even if you are not french and a BattleTech fan, don't hesitate to keep this PDF on you hard drive, I've made it with love and would like to see it living as much as possible.


